title: Jen Psaki at Code 2022
summary:
Former White House Press Secretary Jen Psaki speaks with Kara Swisher at Code 2022. They discuss Psaki's new career at MSNBC, the state of news, and her time in the White House.
Recorded on September 8th in Los Angeles.
